	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="loadlevel SCL_Main_A ; goto 833 -47 -25&#xD;&#xA;The Chosen Three cinematic will play first and set up some important stuff. After this, the dialog may start in several ways: 1 - get spotted by the (neutral) enemies in the boss chamber; 2 - start combat with anyone in Ketheric's combat group; 3 - free Nightsong from her cage (this should pull you into combat with her). Before triggering the dialog, the player might kill Isobel from stealth or destroy Nightsong's cage.&#xD;&#xA;Use the debug commands mentioned in the Act2_COL_KethericShowdown goal." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="516" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This dialog plays at the start of the Ketheric boss fight in the Colony. There are numerous permutations here: Nightsong being dead or alive, freed from her soul cage (through stealth before being spotted); Isobel being absent or tadpoled or tadpoled and killed (in the boss chamber) before entering the dialog; Jaheira being present here (and spotted) or being absent." />
			<children>
				<node id="defaultAttitudes">
					<children>
